    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>''I was in a mall walking by the arcade and I saw these kids playing D.D.R., and I was just stunned. There were all these kids dancing and sweating and actually standing in line and paying money to be physically active.''</p>
        <p>LINDA M. CARSON, a physical education professor, on the video game Dance Dance Revolution. [A18]</p>
